{"tid":1756717,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［2020選戰］地方選區、功能組別懶人包","createTime":"2019-11-26T07:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T18:33:15.000Z","uid":54695,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6207ebc348d0b7cfdcdbc68c2067cf9f1835c1","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:11:34.000Z","msg":"係時候打第二場選戰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個post最後打咗呢篇，應該唔多人睇到，所以重post。<br />\n<br />\n拿，今次趕唔切嘅巴絲唔緊要，下年立法會先係重中之中，提提大家：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下年本冊7月25號後出、所以2020年7月25或之前夠18就可以喺下年登記做選民<br />\n<br />\n新登記嘅deadline係 5月2<br />\n改資料嘅deadline係4月2<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有，有功能組別資格嘅朋友，deadline 都係同上面一樣：<br />\n<br />\n新登記呢張：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0wFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=73c00949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n改界別（傳統a去傳統b；超區去傳統都係呢張）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0wFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=3ccce82e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身有得投超級區議會但又想做傳統轉功能組別的話，咁你可以上網搵吓資料，睇吓上一屆你嗰個界別嘅當選人係咩派別嘅，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1496524/一次過睇晒28個功能界別當選名單%E3%80%80%E3%80%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1496524%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%9D%87%E6%99%9228%E5%80%8B%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%25E3%2580%2580%25E3%2580%2580&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0wFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=d4cdefc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1496524/一次過睇晒28個功能界別當選名單%E3%80%80%E3%80%80</a><br />\n<br />\n如果係非建制，咁就冇懸念轉去功能組別；<br />\n<br />\n如果係建制派，就最好睇吓有冇多於一個候選人參加，有就易啲，叫身邊同一界別嘅人一齊轉做FC同投票；如果冇就盡可能推一個人出去選，唔好畀佢自動當選。<br />\n<br />\n睇返數據，16嗰屆有12個人係零票自動當選，雖然比12年少咗4個，不過咁輸咗個議席堅唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真，成敗得失係在於功能組別，掌握地區選舉議席你只係掌握個否決權，只有掌握埋功能組別你先至可以有say，到時動議廢除功能組別就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實啲咁講，上面嗰段就ff嘅啫，最緊要都係出嚟投，同埋非建制各派別間嘅協調。要贏我哋一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢個係副任務<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義士唔係condom</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1f84c31941dcba118e4af321e5f21fabd2232635","tid":1756717,"uid":160795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"大家好！想同大家介紹一個新 Channel- FundHKers<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKersFund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKersFund&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0wFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=aaf3686f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKersFund</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家平時捐錢捐開邊到？<br />\n星火？立場？<br />\n但其實香港仲有好多機構要大家支持！Channel入面會不定期Share唔同類型嘅機構同眾籌比大家課金。<br />\n<br />\nAdmin會Factcheck眾籌嘅可信程度，認為可信同有急切性先會推比大家！<br />\n<br />\n當然捐唔捐 捐幾多 由自己選擇<br />\n就算能力所限都可以Share比身邊朋友。總之一句到尾，香港人撐香港人！"},{"pid":"15c4e5c9cc733af7a8103879c7f1e0102cf66079","tid":1756717,"uid":327469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">區議會大奇跡日！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">感謝所有不分化，不割席既選民！<br />\n你地叻叻豬！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6f234a1ce4a6576c70fe0acf23f56b606f1f89d7","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 功能組別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另一位巴打開嘅整合post<br />\n<br />\n(重開) [整合] 所有29個功能界別選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90af3391870c75a7573a3b85eea8c97a2321b5b2","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"推10連"},{"pid":"9e1b3518163b7e733cdac3c7d1aae92c8f4025e6","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90af3391870c75a7573a3b85eea8c97a2321b5b2","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"推10連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0886b73558aa61ab12ba1dcd61cc062a8cde9ba5","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e1b3518163b7e733cdac3c7d1aae92c8f4025e6","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90af3391870c75a7573a3b85eea8c97a2321b5b2","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"推10連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e31241f867a127eceb1a52227f0976ccaea4964c","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0886b73558aa61ab12ba1dcd61cc062a8cde9ba5","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e1b3518163b7e733cdac3c7d1aae92c8f4025e6","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90af3391870c75a7573a3b85eea8c97a2321b5b2","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"推10連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"3"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"44861a35d021d456a18a398ea572923638a57cf4","tid":1756717,"uid":54695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,